metadata.name: Dream unicorn #1
metadata.description:
Despite its seriousness, this unicorn is still beautiful and fascinating. Their mane and tail are long and flowing, blowing gently in the wind. Although he doesn't smile or show much emotion, his presence inspires respect and admiration.

In short, this serious unicorn walking in the cotton candy grass is a stunning and captivating image. Her regal appearance and purposeful gait suggest she is a powerful and wise creature, and her presence inspires awe and reverence.
